inputs are dimensionless t/M and r/M. For parabolic QK, rdot is solved \
automatically from En == 0; parabolicVelocitySign chooses its sign. If no \
real solution exists for that sign, the calculation reports an error.\
\>", "Text",ExpressionUUID->"185d85cc-441b-0847-8497-015020cf8994"],

